client.model

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • client.model.Player

  • public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
    Player class contains all the information for each individual player in the game.
    Domain: 0-5 settlements, 0-4 cities, 0-15 roads
    Author:
    Epper Marshall
